title: Hi-Tech Data Processing Sci-Fi Sound Effects
description: 170 professionally designed data processing, high tech, sci-fi sound effects!
longDescription:
Youtube Demo: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZlDUTz_wBfI


With DATA sound library, Sound Response brings you a cutting edge collection of meticulously designed hi-tech data processing and readout sci-fi sound effects! 


If you’re looking for those futuristic-sounding, hi-tech interface sound effects, and the sounds of sci-fi computer readouts, calculations, sensors, and scanning sound effects, this soundpack will provide you with a diverse arsenal of various high tech data processing sound effects to suit your needs.


With DATA sound library at your disposal you’ll have the right audio tool to create that sophisticated, futuristic, sci-fi vibe for your game, movie, trailer, video, or any other project that you’re working on!


DATA - Interface Data Processing Sound Effects List


If you like the sound of DATA sound library be sure to check out Binary Code 2 sound library that features 1000 brand new UI sounds, and also the most massive and the most diverse interface sound library from Sound Response to this date – Binary Code 3 – Interface Multiverse that features whopping 1300 (2.3GB) professionally designed brand new HUD & UI sound effects!
